      <deliverable type="reader">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Nodes/IndexRetrieveNode.cs â€” added `SubjectScope` config field + `BuildSubjectScopeFilter` helper; `MapToProjection` reads `scope` ComplexType into new `InsightRowScope` POCO</deliverable>
      <deliverable type="config">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Options/AiSearchOptions.cs â€” added `DualWriteScopeMatterId` toggle (default true)</deliverable>
