      <deliverable type="tests">tests/unit/Sprk.Bff.Api.Tests/Services/Ai/Nodes/IndexRetrieveNodeSubjectScopeTests.cs â€” 13 tests (hybrid OR-filter generation + canonical narrow-filter + OData escape + composition with other narrowing dimensions)</deliverable>
      <deliverable type="bicep">No Bicep change required â€” `loadJsonContent('schemas/â€¦')` picks up new schema fields automatically; existing search-index.bicep PUT is idempotent</deliverable>
    </deliverables>

    <quality-gates>
      <gate name="build">PASS â€” dotnet build src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/ : 0 errors, 0 new warnings (after applying parallel-task collision fix for InsightsModule.cs line 83 â€” see D6-D6)</gate>
