      <gate name="nfr-08">PASS â€” Phase 1 matter-subject queries filter by `scope/matterId eq 'â€¦'`. Reader OR-filter emits `(scope/matterId eq â€¦ or (scope/entityType eq 'matter' and scope/entityId eq â€¦))` regardless of dual-write flag, so Phase 1 Observations remain queryable.</gate>
